code: @Override public Class<?> getObjectType() {     return (this.transactionManager != null ? this.transactionManager.getClass() : JtaTransactionManager.class). }

static String resolveJtaTransactionManagerClassName() {     if (weblogicPresent) {         return WEBLOGIC_JTA_TRANSACTION_MANAGER_CLASS_NAME.     } else if (webspherePresent) {         return WEBSPHERE_TRANSACTION_MANAGER_CLASS_NAME.     } else {         return JTA_TRANSACTION_MANAGER_CLASS_NAME.     } }
